Once upon a time , in a forest there lived  a monkey who resided on a jamoon tree,which was on the banks of a river, 
in the same forest, there lived a crocodile and his wife. One day the crocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree,
he kindhearted monkey offered him some fruits. The crocodile came back the next day for more fruits, as he loved them. As days passed by,
 the crodile and the monkey became good friends.

one day, the monkey sent some fruits for the crocodile's wife. she ate the fruits and liked them, but wsa jealous as she didnt like her
husband spending time withe the monkey. she told her husbane, "if the fruits are so juicy,i wonder howsweet the monkeys heart would be. get me the 
heart of the monkey. the crocodile was not willing to kill his friend, but he had no choice. 